+# DispatchInputTouchEventParams Object
+
+* `kind` string - Can be `touch`.
+* `type` string - Touch event phase to dispatch. Can be `touchStart`,
+  `touchEnd`, `touchMove`, or `touchCancel`.
+* `touchPoints` [DispatchInputTouchPoint[]](dispatch-input-touch-point.md) (optional) -
+  Touch points participating in this request.
+* `modifiers` Integer (optional) - Bit field of active modifiers using the
+  Chrome DevTools Protocol layout: Alt=1, Ctrl=2, Meta=4, Shift=8.
+* `timestamp` number (optional) - Event timestamp in seconds since the Unix
+  epoch. The current event time is used when omitted.
diff --git a/docs/api/structures/dispatch-input-touch-point.md b/docs/api/structures/dispatch-input-touch-point.md
